      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable transportation option for those on a budget. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car shows significant signs of wear consistent with its age, including several paint chips, minor interior stains, and a slight suspension creak. While it runs and drives well enough for daily commutes, a new owner should expect to perform some minor maintenance and cosmetic touch-ups in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car without the premium price of a mint-condition model.",
